      <description>&lt;h5 id=&#34;posted-on-july-24-2021&#34;&gt;Posted on July 24, 2021&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;the-next-project&#34;&gt;The next project&amp;hellip;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Now that I&amp;rsquo;ve got most of the website running and working (the art side
can wait for another time), I think it&amp;rsquo;s about time
I get working on some actual projects. It&amp;rsquo;s been a while since I&amp;rsquo;ve used
Unity so I think it&amp;rsquo;s about time I get refreshed and get started on a game.
I probably won&amp;rsquo;t be able to update the blog until I get some significant
progress done and have some images/gifs to show for it. So with that said,
onto the planning phase!&lt;/p&gt;</description>
