    <item>
      <title>The beginning of the website</title>
      <link>https://shutowl.github.io/blog/beginning-of-website/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Jul 2021 21:54:05 -0700</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://shutowl.github.io/blog/beginning-of-website/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h5 id=&#34;posted-on-july-19-2021&#34;&gt;Posted on July 19, 2021&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Today I felt like making a website. I mean, I had always meant to do it at one point,
but I had always put it off until today. &lt;a href=&#34;https://pages.github.com/&#34;&gt;Github Pages&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;https://gohugo.io/&#34;&gt;Hugo&lt;/a&gt; 
made it seem like it would be pretty easy to make one, but boy was I wrong. I spent pretty much all day trying to get it
to work, but at least it seems to work now, even if it does look pretty barebones right now.
I still gotta learn a bunch of stuff to make this blog look a little better, so I&amp;rsquo;ll work
on this website for now before diving into other things.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://shutowl.github.io/images/pochigga.png&#34; alt=&#34;maidpochita&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I also need to figure out how to format images like this on these sites too lmao&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>About me</title>
      <link>https://shutowl.github.io/about/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Jul 2021 21:49:09 -0700</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://shutowl.github.io/about/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h3 id=&#34;who-are-you&#34;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Who are you?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nice to meet you! My name&amp;rsquo;s Qicheng Shuto, but most people just call me Kenneth since it&amp;rsquo;s easier to pronouce.
As of 2021, I&amp;rsquo;m a student majoring in CS, but I grew up making music and art on the side.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;what-are-your-goals&#34;&gt;&lt;em&gt;What are your goals?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;First off, I still need projects to fill this portfolio, so the priority will be small fleshed-out games.
The art side of the page still needs to be worked on before I make it public and even before that I need
some actual drawings too.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;any-hobbies&#34;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Any hobbies?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Besides art and music, I&amp;rsquo;m just a nerd who plays games and uses &lt;a href=&#34;https://myanimelist.net/profile/kshut&#34;&gt;anime&lt;/a&gt; and JPop
to learn Japanese. 
すみませんでした。。。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;why-shutowl-and-kshut&#34;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Why &amp;ldquo;shutowl&amp;rdquo; and &amp;ldquo;kshut&amp;rdquo;?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;shutowl&amp;rdquo; just combines my last name &amp;ldquo;Shuto&amp;rdquo; and owl and pronouced like &amp;ldquo;shoo-towel&amp;rdquo;.
I thought owls were pretty cool back in the day and I related quite a bit to them.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&amp;ldquo;kshut&amp;rdquo; was a so-called &amp;ldquo;rapper name&amp;rdquo; that my friends came up with a long time ago.
It also just combines my first and last name and it just kinda stuck with me.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
They&amp;rsquo;re both kinda dumb now that I think about it.&lt;/p&gt;
